<p class="ql-align-justify">好奇宝宝miniko</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">已经第一时间冲去打卡啦~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200827/c290b5a7f4c44a1fb53f136e312c610f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">成都的好吃嘴们，分两类</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一类是哪些店火就去哪里一类是哪稀奇就去凑热闹</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">牛杂火锅、鸭血火锅、土豆火锅</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">卤味火锅、集市火锅、市井火锅</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">...</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">成都的火锅五花八门但红茶火锅，miniko还是第一次吃！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200827/2328e189fa98472ba3ea09746bfc7039.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>TA是红茶火锅的开创者</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>底料由牛油+红茶炒制</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
